r disciplined catalystfocused absolute return strategy” michael singer chief executive officer of ramius says samantha has proven herself an astute and skilled investor and we believe her talents are wellsuited to markets where alpha generation is in short supply as samanthas partner we are committed to doing everything we can to build a successful business together we believe that samantha’s formidable investment skills and talents will benefit our institutional and high net worth clients worldwide margate will initially manage proprietary capital for cowen and will launch a commingled product in coming months like this article  get the free daily newsletter print email furtherreading from hedgeweek global advisors jersey launches crypto fund tue    gabelli merger plus trust now trading on lse wed    megatrust investments launches yangtze fund iv wed    crystal century investment launches liquid alternative multiasset fund tue    crown capital partners announces usdm upsizing of crown capital fund iv fri    from our other sites private advisors seventh small company pe fund hits hard cap wed    nasdaq stock market welcomed  new etps in q  tue    lyxor launches infrastructure income etfs tue    bouwinvest invests eur million in hines paneuropean core fund tue    three new ishares equity and bond etfs launch on xetra tue    features guides  guide to setting up an alternative investment fund in europe wed   blogs building investment fund structures  from startup to stardom tue   before you head to the beach… fri   the cftc provides more robust protection to whistleblowers wed   awards hedgeweek global awards  thu   special reports cybersecurity in europe  wed   mitigating compliance risk for pe managers thu   sei blockchain  building ecosystems in financial services fri   mifid ii meeting the compliance challenge sat   investment opportunities in infrastructure debt thu   events total alts thursday september     catalyst cap intro ls equity  event driven investing mon